      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/small-cap-funds-in-india-see-first-outflow-after-over-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度小盘基金出现自 2021 年 9 月以来首次月度资金流出，监管机构发出潜在繁荣警告后，这些公司的股价暴跌。]]></description>
