      <title>德国在华企业称其受到当地人的不公平竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/german-firms-in-china-see-unfair-competition-from-local-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三分之二在华经营的德国公司表示，他们面临市场不公平竞争，这一问题可能会推高其成本并侵蚀利润率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/german-firms-in-china-see-unfair-competition-from-local-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管竞争对手因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎，宝马电动汽车销量仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马公司其核心品牌的全电动汽车销量在第一季度大幅增长，表现优于特斯拉和大众等竞争对手，后者一直在努力应对疲软的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行维持利率不变，与政府的分歧加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thai-central-bank-holds-rate-deepening-rift-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行周三维持利率不变，突显货币政策支持经济增长的局限性，尤其是在财政环境宽松的情况下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thai-central-bank-holds-rate-deepening-rift-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
